'''Isorpian Raiders''' were a group of beings who attacked a small village in both the ''[[Jedi Men From Baronis]]'' and ''[[Two Jedi Men From Baronis]]'' [[Jediboh Opera]] plays. They were driven back by two [[Bantha/Legends|bantha]] [[Merchant/Legends|salesmen]] who were mistakenly identified as [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]].

